{"tid":1007212,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"好唔開心... 男朋友讚第個女人靚","createTime":"2019-02-03T15:12:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-03T16:58:40.000Z","uid":431,"like":4,"dislike":35,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"e1499fbed3cd9c7e19c612f5b13be21929ed711d","tid":1007212,"uid":431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-03T15:12:12.000Z","msg":"我男朋友好少讚女仔靚<br />\n每次佢轉新公司我都循例問佢有無靚女 佢次次都答無<br />\n今次我同樣地問佢 佢答&quot;無乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />&quot;<br />\n咁即係有啦!!!!<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n追問下原來佢覺得公司秘書靚 仲話係ceo福利 即係好似好羨慕個ceo咁款<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n之後我問佢個秘書係咪著低胸短裙高爭鞋 佢死都唔肯答<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 明知我嬲都唔答!!!! <br />\n佢話佢哋唔會有交流 我問咁即係有交流就會鍾意佢啦!!!!!!!!!<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n佢又叫我唔好亂諗 即係無否認啦!!!!!!!!!<br />\n<br />\n我估個秘書係低胸短裙長腿<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我呢家決定減返肥 應該減幾磅就ok!!!!!<br />\n之後著低胸短裙出街俾人望當報復!!!<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 睇佢以後仲敢唔敢讚人!!!<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"789df632266071acf2d2b6111bc4789102fbfbc2","tid":1007212,"uid":76697,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-03T15:12:52.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ac83e202a405f319a011b44e5b609ac0e84d12e6","tid":1007212,"uid":56204,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-03T15:14:16.000Z","msg":"55"},{"pid":"4d84f75651e9959237ec8a4c1685e003114426b7","tid":1007212,"uid":64318,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-03T15:14:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6da27849db80a196bd727c6b414e738c2e7c674e","tid":1007212,"uid":23758,"li